EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 2100Z DAILY
   16 THRU 18 OCT IN AREA WITHIN 90 MILES OF
   57-20.7N 010-16.2W. VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER
   AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 182200Z OCT 17.
